snippet.title: Ma Cheon Ru - Mame 0 161 -
snippet.description:
Ma Cheon Ru is a new game available to play on Mame 0.161 from the korean company Semicom. This game consist in make rows of 3 same items to remove the screen of them.

There is no know ports of this game.
